Title: Section 1 [recto]
AltTitle.translated: The Bandlet of Righteousness, The Way of Heaven
Description.note: 1 በስመ: አብ: ወወልድ: ወመንፈስ: ቅዱስ: ፩  አምላክ ጸሎት በእንተ ልፋፈ ጽድቅ ወመጽሐፈ ድኅነት ዘወሀባ አብ ለማርያም እንተ ጸሓፋ በእዴሁ ቅድሳት እምቅድመ ይትወለድ ክርስቶስ በሥጋ ; In the name of the Father the Son and the Holy Spirit One God, prayer about Bandlet of Righteousness and book of salvation,(God the) Father wrote in his holy hand and gave it to Mary before Christ was born in the flesh…|~|Section 1 of 6 of a folded concertina.
